      <div type="letter" xml:id="d4e38">
        <pb n="1" facs="0012_000117_000211_0001.jpg" xml:id="d4e39"/>
        <p>David Burford</p>
        <p>Dixon Creek</p>
        <p>Smith Co</p>
        <p>Tenn.</p>
        <p>From Perkins, Campbell &amp; Co</p>
        <p>Rec'd 29 Aug, 1853</p>
        <p><unclear reason="illegible" resp="SLJ">Ackg</unclear> $5,000 -</p>
        <pb n="2" facs="0012_000117_000211_0002.jpg" xml:id="d4e57"/>
        <p>"Mail"</p>
        <p>New Orleans August 16th 1853</p>
        <p>David Burford Esq</p>
        <p>Dixon Springs, Smith Co, Tenn,</p>
        <p>Dear Sir,</p>
        <p>Your account has Credit Five Thousand Dollars $5.000 - for W. B. Shaphard Chk for that amount received in July of 10th <unclear reason="illegible" resp="SLJ">July</unclear> Just at hand. We note Your <unclear reason="illegible" resp="SLJ">mistrusting</unclear> about investing that amount @ 8% for undoubted Security. On 4 Nov <unclear reason="illegible" resp="SLJ">time</unclear>. Our Mr. Perkins will write you further on this subject when well - He is now sick</p>
        <p>Very Respy</p>
        <p>Perkins, Campbell &amp; Co</p>
        <p>for P. L. <unclear reason="illegible" resp="SLJ">Kennen</unclear>
            </p>
      </div>
    </body>
